{"tid":1427723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論戰 我地再做得醒目啲","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:16:24.000Z","uid":104507,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f3f520f6b6ea45a6b3ad2d9f60d9fb762ac366","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"睇返黑警最近兩日嘅小動作<br />\n知道輿論戰又一觸即發<br />\n<br />\n如果發生任何爭執或衝突<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">要有手足即刻變身&quot;記者&quot;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">確保有人紀錄低事件嘅前因後果</span></span><br />\n減低只有片面影片流出 送材料比對家<br />\n因為我相信大家唔會無差別攻擊市民<br />\n所以大家切記<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">出師有名 搶對家道德高底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出到嚟嘅各位手足<br />\n無論我地內心嬲到猶如洪水猛獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係鏡頭面前一定要做返雞蛋 做柔弱嘅一方</span></span><br />\n和理非、爸爸媽媽會更有理據繼續支持同&quot;守護孩子&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩火無問題 但一定要對準玩</span></span><br />\n例如 垃圾❎ 宿舍❎ 路過TK車、市民❎<br />\n火魔法✅ 警局✅ 黑警✅ 黑社會✅<br />\n<br />\n最近紅媒開始對準嚟製造輿論<br />\n而好多淺黃無可避免會動搖咗<br />\n無可否認 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">對家製造輿論同文宣有一手</span></span><br />\n我地更要向對家學習 <span style=\"color: orange;\">打對等輿論戰 製造對等文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將文宣打入藍色區域<br />\n<br />\n脫離同溫層</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha9MS6k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa9MS6k.png&h=9f733659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"e437a1b94641d896de4f230b0a1085a6138b40cb","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"94e4aaab6d2ff4dd89f8fe81d6341eb97e823158","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e2459563baba269657dc8d00bbe11ca2975b58ed","tid":1427723,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"60561c4c27f5a06d0e70548701263b79b12e1435","tid":1427723,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQoazRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQoazRf.png&h=236cac31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2cKEhW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2cKEhW.jpg&h=53f4ae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRGfLXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRGfLXW.jpg&h=a6020ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG2R3KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwG2R3KC.jpg&h=ba33973f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4550e42ef08e4f6ff669cc5bf5aa298abfd42107","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"909d2afa7c2bdadc42141a0feea813bd636fc751","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5d44f1512f80fcf11c6c531c09d37ae3e809b987","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"6ffc27701e8daf80b6c2c584406faf3f26512e9f","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"877ea4d712a217b6ddbf9a5608fec80cd84b889e","tid":1427723,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"9"},{